          <Image
            src={privatePracticeHeaderImg}
            width={1280}
            alt="Image of two professionals discussing"
            class="software-img"
            style="height: auto;"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="padding-global padding-section-medium cc-prof Drowning">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <h2 class="section-heading-nx">
        <strong>Admissions Teams Are Drowning in Manual Work</strong>
      </h2>
      <p class="subparagraph-nx">
        Your admissions coordinators shouldn't spend half their day stuck on
        hold with insurance companies. Every minute wasted on manual
        verification is a minute a patient waits for life-changing treatment.
        When referrals get lost in spreadsheets and leads slip through the
        cracks, you're not just losing revenue - you're missing opportunities to
        help people in crisis.
      </p>

      <p class="subparagraph-nx">
        Without unified behavioral health admissions software, your team
        operates in the dark. Marketing can't prove ROI. Admissions can't track
        conversion rates. Leadership lacks the visibility needed for strategic
        decisions. Meanwhile, competitors with modern systems are converting
        leads faster and growing smarter.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="padding-global padding-section-medium cc-prof CRMSoftware">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <h1 class="section-heading-nx">
        Healthcare CRM Software That Actually Works for Behavioral Health
      </h1>
      <p class="subparagraph-nx">
        Navix CRM eliminates the bottlenecks that slow down admissions. Our
        addiction treatment CRM combines lead management, automated insurance
        verification, and referral tracking into one seamless platform - no
        juggling multiple systems or waiting on integrations that never quite
        work.
      </p>
      <div class="subsections-nx">
        <div class="subsection-nx">
          <h2 class="subheading-nx">
            Convert Faster With Intelligent Automation
          </h2>
          <p class="subparagraph-nx">
            Automated workflows reduce time-to-admission by up to 60%. When a
            lead comes in, Navix automatically routes it to the right
            coordinator, triggers insurance verification, and keeps everyone on
            track with smart reminders. Every second counts when someone is
            ready for treatment - Navix ensures your team never misses a moment.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="subsection-nx">
          <h2 class="subheading-nx">Manage Smarter With Unified Visibility</h2>
          <p class="subparagraph-nx">
            Whether you run one facility or oversee a multi-state network, Navix
            gives you complete oversight without sacrificing local flexibility.
            Our multi-location healthcare management dashboards show you exactly
            what's happening across your organization while empowering each
            facility to operate efficiently.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="subsection-nx">
          <h2 class="subheading-nx">
            Grow Confidently With Data-Driven Insights
          </h2>
          <p class="subparagraph-nx">
            Stop guessing which marketing channels work. Navix tracks every lead
            from source to admission, showing you which campaigns, referral
            partners, and team members drive results. Make budget decisions
            based on actual cost per admission - not assumptions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="padding-global padding-section-medium cc-prof">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <h1 class="navixh-heading">Everything Your Admissions Team Needs</h1>

      <div class="navixh-subsections">
        <div class="navixh-subsection">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Lead and Referral Management That Never Drops the Ball
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Your referral management system healthcare needs to handle
            complexity without creating chaos. Navix provides full pipeline
            visibility with color-coded stages, customizable workflows, and
            drag-and-drop simplicity. See every lead from inquiry to admission
            in one unified dashboard.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Intelligent lead routing automatically assigns new inquiries based
            on program type, bed availability, insurance type, and location. No
            more manual sorting or delayed responses. Navix ensures the right
            coordinator gets each lead immediately, improving response times and
            conversion rates.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Track every referral source - physician networks, alumni, detox
            centers, sober living facilities, and professional partners. Measure
            referral quality and conversion rates to nurture your most valuable
            relationships. Our mobile app keeps coordinators connected whether
            they're at networking events, visiting partners, or working
            remotely.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixh-subsection">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Automated Insurance Verification That Saves Hours Daily
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Insurance verification shouldn't take 2-4 hours per patient. Our
            automated insurance verification software connects with 1,200+
            payers for real-time eligibility checks. Get detailed benefits
            breakdowns - in-network versus out-of-network rates, deductibles,
            co-insurance, out-of-pocket maximums, and pre-authorization
            requirements - in minutes instead of hours.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Once verification completes, Navix automatically triggers the next
            steps: scheduling assessments, sending financial agreements, and
            coordinating transportation. No manual handoffs means no delays. VOB
            data flows directly into your billing system, reducing claim denials
            and accelerating reimbursement.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixh-subsection">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Campaign Performance Tracking That Proves Marketing ROI
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Marketing directors need concrete data, not vague metrics. Navix
            provides multi-channel attribution across Google Ads, Meta
            advertising, organic search, referral partners, events, and direct
            mail. Calculate your true cost per admission by channel and
            campaign. Compare Google Ads performance against referral
            partnerships and organic traffic to make informed budget decisions.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            UTM parameter tracking captures performance down to individual ad
            campaigns, keywords, and landing pages. Test messaging variations
            and optimize continuously. Not all leads are equal - Navix tracks
            lead quality metrics like show rates, conversion rates, length of
            stay, and insurance acceptance rates by source, helping you invest
            in channels that deliver high-intent, high-value patients.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixh-subsection">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Multi-Location Management Built for Growth
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Managing multiple facilities shouldn't mean juggling separate
            systems. Navix provides enterprise-level oversight with
            location-specific flexibility. View aggregate performance across all
            locations in real time - admissions volume, conversion rates,
            average time-to-admission, and team productivity.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Customize admissions workflows, VOB requirements, and team
            permissions by location while maintaining corporate visibility.
            Support residential, IOP, PHP, detox, and sober living programs
            within one system. Generate executive reports that roll up data from
            every location for board presentations and investor reporting.
            Role-based permissions ensure appropriate access for corporate
            leadership, regional directors, facility administrators, and
            front-line staff.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixh-subsection">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Analytics That Drive Better Decisions
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Transform admissions data into actionable insights. Monitor
            conversion rates by referral source, lead type, insurance carrier,
            and admissions coordinator. Identify exactly where leads drop off in
            your funnel. Set benchmarks and track improvement over time.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Measure team productivity - calls made, emails sent, follow-ups
            completed, conversions achieved. Identify coaching opportunities and
            recognize top performers. Use historical data to predict patient
            length of stay based on insurance type, program level, and clinical
            presentation, optimizing bed utilization and revenue forecasting.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Build custom dashboards tailored to your leadership team's
            priorities. Track census, pipeline health, referral partner
            activity, marketing ROI, or any combination of metrics. Schedule
            automated reports for weekly, monthly, or quarterly delivery.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="padding-global padding-section-medium cc-prof">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <div class="navixh-subsections">
        <div class="navixhealthcont">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Seamless Integration With Your Existing Technology Stack
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Navix CRM works with the healthcare technology you've already
            invested in - no rip-and-replace required. We integrate with major
