            Billing and RCM integration includes Navix RevFlow, Change
            Healthcare, Waystar, Availity, Office Ally, Kareo, and
            SimplePractice.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Connect your marketing platforms - Google Ads, Meta Business Suite,
            CallRail, HubSpot, Mailchimp, ActiveCampaign, and SEMrush.
            Communication tools include Twilio for SMS and voice, RingCentral,
            Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Slack, and Google Workspace. Insurance
            verification partners include iVerify, Experian Health, Availity,
            Change Healthcare Eligibility, and Waystar.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixhealthcont">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Why Choose Navix Over Generic Healthcare CRMs?
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Generic platforms like Salesforce Health Cloud require months of
            implementation and expensive consultants to configure for behavioral
            health workflows. All-in-one EMR and CRM solutions force you to
            replace your entire clinical system. Navix is the optimal middle
            ground - purpose-built for behavioral health admissions, quick to
            implement, and designed to integrate with your existing tools.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            We're built specifically for behavioral health, include native
            automated VOB, offer native Google and Meta campaign tracking,
            provide unlimited multi-location dashboards, implement in 2-4 weeks
            (not months), use transparent per-user pricing, and assign dedicated
            customer success managers with 24/7 support.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixhealthcont">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Built for Every Role in Your Organization
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Admissions Coordinators manage 50+ leads weekly without missing
            follow-ups. Automated reminders keep them on track, call scripts
            guide conversations, and VOB results appear in seconds. Conversion
            rates increase while handling more leads than ever.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Marketing Directors finally have proof of which campaigns drive
            admissions and which waste budget. Track exact cost per admission by
            channel, ad group, and keyword. Reallocate budget from
            underperforming campaigns to increase qualified leads while reducing
            overall spend.
          </p>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Operations Leaders see everything in one dashboard instead of
            compiling reports from multiple facilities. Real-time corporate
            dashboards update automatically. Compare performance across
            facilities, identify capacity issues before they become problems,
            and make strategic decisions based on actual data instead of
            assumptions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="navixhealthcont">
          <h2 class="navixh-subheading">
            Trusted by 200+ Behavioral Health Facilities Nationwide
          </h2>
          <p class="navixh-paragraph">
            Navix has helped treatment centers cut VOB time by 75%, increase
            conversions by 40% in 90 days, and transform multi-location
            operations. Our clients report happier admissions teams, clearer
            marketing ROI, and better strategic decision-making. With a 4.8/5 G2
            rating based on 127 reviews, we're recognized as the best healthcare
            CRM software for behavioral health.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

